#left_column
  %p.subpage_text
    %strong Pinball Map Apps
  %p.subpage_text 
    We currently have two mobile apps released. One's for the iPhone, and the other is for Android. The iPhone app has just seen the release of version 2 (with some major updates)! And the Android app was recently released!
    %br/
    %br/
    The newest versions of these apps will work for all the regions the website currently covers. You just open the app and then choose where you are located. And they will automatically support the new regions that are added in the future (and you won't need to update).
  %p.subpage_text
    %span Featuring splash artwork by&nbsp;
    =link_to 'Drew Marshall', 'http://workbydrew.com', :class => 'light_blue'
