    %strong iPhone app - version 2
    %p.subpage_text
      \.99 cents on the iTunes store (link to the upper right). The app totally rules.
      %br/
      %br/
      iPhone 4.0 and iPod Touch 3.0 compatible.
  %p.subpage_text
    =link_to 'Click here for iPhone app support (and to see some screenshots).', app_support_path, :class => 'light_blue'
